recommend keep-going -- the SLC product now has both a sovereign-flagship device (Fairphone /e/OS) and a reach device (used Pixel 7a/8a), with the client and audience both widened and the green L1 core untouched. The build-side next step is unchanged and unblocked: Pool P0, which turns L1 into the live L2 broadcast the reach tier is meant to carry.
